# 🔍 KQL Query Snippets (Used in Investigation)

## Identify Compromised User

```kusto
SigninLogs
| where TimeGenerated between (datetime(2026-02-25 21:00:00) .. datetime(2026-02-25 23:00:00))
| where UserDisplayName =~ "Mark Smith"
| distinct UserPrincipalName
```

## Detect MFA Fatigue Attempts

```kusto
SigninLogs
| where UserDisplayName =~ "Mark Smith"
| where ResultType != 0
| summarize Attempts=count() by IPAddress
```

## Identify Attacker IP

```kusto
SigninLogs
| where UserDisplayName =~ "Mark Smith"
| where ResultType == 0
| summarize count() by IPAddress, LocationDetails
```

## Inbox Rule Creation Detection

```kusto
CloudAppEvents
| where ActionType == "New-InboxRule"
| extend raw = parse_json(RawEventData)
| mv-expand params = raw.Parameters
| project TimeGenerated, tostring(params.Name), tostring(params.Value)
```

## Identify Fraud Email

```kusto
EmailEvents
| where SenderFromAddress has "mark"
| where Subject has "invoice"
| project TimeGenerated, RecipientEmailAddress, Subject
```

